metadata.name: Contemplative
metadata.description:
Name: Contemplative
Date: 2021
Location:  Lombok, Indonesia
Edition Size: 1 of 1

'Contemplative' is a 1 of 1 NFT.  It is part of the collection 'Pelican Moods' by international award-winning photographer Alfred Minnaar.

The collection is a beautiful depiction of Australian pelicans showcasing their individuality and unique characters. A snapshot of social diversity through captivating visuals.

The images were photographed in a wildlife park in Lombok, Indonesia, which serves as a refuge for animals rescued from the illegal wildlife trade.
